### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### ============================
### Request a ride
### ============================

### Request ride — should allocate nearest available driver
POST {{baseUrl}}/rides
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pickupLocation": {
    "latitude": 0.0,
    "longitude": 0.0
  }
}

###

### Request second ride — should allocate next nearest driver
POST {{baseUrl}}/rides
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pickupLocation": {
    "latitude": 0.0,
    "longitude": 0.0
  }
}

###

### Missing pickupLocation → expect 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/rides
Content-Type: application/json

{}

###

### Missing latitude → expect 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/rides
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pickupLocation": {
    "longitude": 0.0
  }
}

###

### Missing longitude → expect 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/rides
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pickupLocation": {
    "latitude": 0.0
  }
}

###

### No drivers available → expect 503
### (run this after all drivers are allocated)
POST {{baseUrl}}/rides
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pickupLocation": {
    "latitude": 0.0,
    "longitude": 0.0
  }
}

### ============================
### Complete a ride
### ============================

### Complete a ride — replace {id} with real ride ID
### Driver should become AVAILABLE again
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/rides/{{rideId}}/complete

###

### Complete same ride again → expect 409
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/rides/{{rideId}}/complete

###

### Unknown ride ID → expect 404
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/rides/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/complete
